a "hello world" style web app using sinatra / datamapper / haml

there are three directories for the MVC stuff:
 - models
 - views
 - controllers

and two additional directoriess for house-keeping:
  - db: for the database
  - public: for the css and js and images

this software is covered under the MIT License

see LICENSE for further details
